snippet.title: Duck Life 9 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
It's the moment you've all been waiting for... Duck Life is officially coming back! 

The ducks will return in early 2024 like you've never seen them before. Duck Life 9 will be available on PC, Mac, Switch, Xbox, PS5, iOS and Android
